org.drombler.acp.core.docking

Annotation Type EditorDocking


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=SOURCE)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface EditorDocking
    Registers an editor dockable.

    The annotated editor requires a constructor with a single parameter of type contentType(). The contentType is usually a data handler.

    A new editor dockable will be created for each provided content (see the Docking SPI package for helper classes).
    Author:
    puce
